Watergate : more than the spaghetti net / moderated by Fran Watkins.
PRA Archive #: BC1362 https://www.pacificaradioarchives.org/recording/bc1362

Marty Gellen, Franz Schurmann and Peter Dale Scott discuss the Watergate affair, and the crisis it created in American government.
Date Broadcast on: KPFA, 30 May 1973.
